reportingDefinition: Biopsy and/or cytology specimen reports with a diagnosis of primary non-small cell lung cancer classified into specific hitologic type (squamous cell carcinoma, adenocarcinoma) OR classified as NSCLC-NOS with an explanation included in the pathology report.
